| **Bitcoin (the organism)** | Block subsidies (newly minted BSV) + transaction fees | Energy, hardware, social consensus, network security, distributed body |
| **Miners** | Electrical energy, ASIC hardware, computational work | Block subsidies + transaction fees (denominated in BSV) |
| **Node Operators** | Hardware, bandwidth, storage, maintenance | A trustworthy, independently verified copy of the ledger |
| **Users and Businesses** | Social consensus, demand, liquidity, adoption | A censorship-resistant, tamper-proof store of value and transactional system |
| **Developers** | Code, intellectual labor, protocol maintenance | Reputation, community standing, and the satisfaction of contributing to a transformative system |
| **Humanity (collectively)** | The entire infrastructure of civilization (energy grids, internet, legal systems) | A new monetary layer and universal data infrastructure: provably honest, mathematically enforced, and politically neutral |

